text: Greta Lukjančukė (; born 10 September 1992) is a Lithuanian footballer who plays as a goalkeeper and has appeared for the Lithuania women's national team. ==Career== Lukjančukė has been capped for the Lithuania national team, appearing for the team during the 2019 FIFA Women's World Cup qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * , part 1 * , part 2 * * Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football goalkeepers Category:Lithuanian women's footballers Category:People from Ukmergė Category:Lithuania women's international footballers Category:Gintra Universitetas players
